website_summaries.verdict: An affordable dog food with a mixture of small crunchy and chewy pieces by a well-known brand.
pros: In addition to small, classic kibble, this popular food has chewy bits that dogs love
Chicken is one of the top ingredients, and provides quality protein
Probiotics promote healthy digestion, while omega fatty acids improve coats
cons: Some dogs love the chewy bits so much that they are slow to eat the crunchy pieces

customer_reviews.title: Finally!!!!!!!

I would like a fresh bag sent as a replacement. Short of that I will get this food elsewhere if Amazon doesn't make it good. I might add that his has never happened to me or my dog before, and I'm quite upset.

"The question is," said Alice, "whether you can make words mean so many different things."

customer_reviews.title: What you might not know
customer_reviews.text: So this food was good in flavor for my dog, she ate it very happily. Although, it made her poop twice a day and be pretty soft. I discovered that mixing meats with dry food is dangerous for your pets! They digest the foods at different rates (meat first, dry food later) which is very straining for their stomach. I have become more aware of the damages of dry food in all but I thought I should let others who don’t know, know. If you want to feed your dogs dry food, don’t use this one! Use the regular focus or any other which is only the dry food.

product_meta.title: Purina Pro Plan With Probiotics Small Breed Dry Dog Food, SAVOR Shredded Blend Chicken & Rice Formula - 6 lb. Bag
product_meta.description: Cater to your small breed dog's need for high quality protein and nutrient dense meals by feeding him Purina Pro Plan SAVOR Shredded Blend Chicken & Rice Small Breed Formula adult dry dog food. With real chicken as the #1 ingredient, this super premium, highly digestible dry dog food delivers outstanding nutrition to help keep your small breed dog at his very best. An optimal protein to fat ratio helps your best friend maintain an ideal body condition, while vitamin A and linoleic acid, an omega 6 fatty acid, help support a healthy coat and skin. Natural prebiotic fiber, sourced from wheat bran, and guaranteed live probiotics provide digestive and immune system support. This formula's tender shredded pieces are mixed with crunchy kibble in a size that's easy for his smaller mouth to manage. Manufactured in Purina owned U.S. facilities, Purina Pro Plan SAVOR Shredded Chicken & Rice adult small breed dog food is a 100 percent complete and balanced meal for your adult dog under 20 pounds. Calorie Content (fed) - 4034 kcal/kg, 393 kcal/cup
